  "detailed_description": "Mow-down at the hoedown!  <br><br>Pack your bags and move to the idyllic countryside. Pay no heed to the nuclear fallout – it adds a lovely glow to your complexion! Upsides – everyone wants a piece of you! Downsides – everyone wants a piece of you... <br> <br>Grab your blunderbuss and get ready for twin-stick, bullet-hell, roguelite, corn-chuckin' action game that will last until the cows come home! As any self-respecting farmer would: Farm. Marry. Kill. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sow and harvest as many fast-growing crops as you can before the day is done to earn a huge profit. Purchase weapons and items in town at the end of each day. Celebrate the end of each season with special shops and rewards. <br></li><li>Permanently Upgrade your farming and fighting abilities. Earn a payout each run that can be used on permanent improvements and unlocks. <br></li><li>Progress through the years with ramping difficulty and even greater rewards! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Befriend an entourage of pig pals, chicken chums, and cow colleagues to automate farming tasks. Woo and marry a kindred spirit from the local town to fight and farm alongside you. <br></li><li>Unlock new characters, spouses, difficulties, and permanent upgrades. Most importantly, you can unlock many cats to permanently roam your homestead (yes, you can pet them).</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defend your crops from unforgiving nightly attackers looking to rampage your hard-earned harvest. <br></li><li>Fight challenging bosses each season until you reach the final season - the Nuclear Winter.  <br></li><li>Explore the far reaches of the biomes to find useful relics of farms long past. Powerful loot increases your farming abilities and helps you fight enemies. </li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Mow-down at the hoedown!  <br><br>Pack your bags and move to the idyllic countryside. Pay no heed to the nuclear fallout – it adds a lovely glow to your complexion! Upsides – everyone wants a piece of you! Downsides – everyone wants a piece of you... <br> <br>Grab your blunderbuss and get ready for twin-stick, bullet-hell, roguelite, corn-chuckin' action game that will last until the cows come home! As any self-respecting farmer would: Farm. Marry. Kill. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/b2a95963ea0038e032897e735a7ed7e1.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sow and harvest as many fast-growing crops as you can before the day is done to earn a huge profit. Purchase weapons and items in town at the end of each day. Celebrate the end of each season with special shops and rewards. <br></li><li>Permanently Upgrade your farming and fighting abilities. Earn a payout each run that can be used on permanent improvements and unlocks. <br></li><li>Progress through the years with ramping difficulty and even greater rewards! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/e179f8dca8a9a62f0adf3c4a4ea379aa.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Befriend an entourage of pig pals, chicken chums, and cow colleagues to automate farming tasks. Woo and marry a kindred spirit from the local town to fight and farm alongside you. <br></li><li>Unlock new characters, spouses, difficulties, and permanent upgrades. Most importantly, you can unlock many cats to permanently roam your homestead (yes, you can pet them).</li></ul> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.poster.avif?t=1766091257\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.webm?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/757320/extras/ea0eed8c844c960fea68292cb9501ab8.mp4?t=1766091257\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Defend your crops from unforgiving nightly attackers looking to rampage your hard-earned harvest. <br></li><li>Fight challenging bosses each season until you reach the final season - the Nuclear Winter.  <br></li><li>Explore the far reaches of the biomes to find useful relics of farms long past. Powerful loot increases your farming abilities and helps you fight enemies. </li></ul>",
